  <description><![CDATA[<p>The brand new Hyatt Centric has been built to the highest possible standards and opened its doors in December 2017. It's perfect for anybody looking to combine luxury with the extensive spa facilities with tastefully decorated surroundings in the bars and restaurants and easy access to the slopes. The bedrooms are spacious and all have a balcony with mountain views. Meals are taken in the H40 restaurant and there is also an Italian trattoria (La Travola) offering refinded and local organic cuisine with a grill and pizza oven (supplement payable). Relax in the H40 Bar with fireplace and which serves its famous Elephant beer or try the Surus Lounge Bar with its cosy atmosphere and panoramic views. 7 night stays from Sunday to Sunday are available along with shorter Heliskiing Trips in low season from 13th January. Heliskiing Trips include flights, transfers, 3 or 4 night stays on half board, lift passes, ski rental, 2 heliski drops per person and a welcome drink on your arrival. Available dates are 13th January to 9th February, 4th to 23rd March and 7th to 21st April. Stays from 30th January will also receive a VIP first tracks trip so you can be first on the groomed slopes between 7.30 and 9am.</p>]]></description>
